'.\" -*- nroff -*-
.TH KAFSCTL 1 "2026-01-28" "kafs 0.0.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
kafsctl \- query runtime stats from a mounted kafs filesystem
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kafsctl
.B stats
.I mountpoint
.RB [ --json ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B kafsctl
queries a running
.BR kafs (1)
instance via a FUSE ioctl and prints filesystem/HRL statistics, including dedup-related indicators.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B stats
Print current stats for the mounted filesystem at
.IR mountpoint .
Use
.B --json
to emit machine-readable JSON.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kafs (1)
.SH AUTHOR
kafs project.
